data.description: MINT condition Holdcroft Heights 2 bedroom, 1 bath BLOCK home! This home has been meticulously cared for, in 2023 the home received a new Roof, Upgraded R38 insulation, Soffits, Facia, Gutters, and re-pipe to include a new 40 gal water heater, along with the new modern Bathroom renovation. In 2022  new flooring was installed, along with new appliances including a washer and dryer, and the home was painted inside and out. Other upgrades consist of 3cm granite countertops, newer windows, and doors. The property has a 360 security system that can be viewed from your smartphone or tablet. The backyard is fully fenced in for privacy and has 2 storage sheds, The 16X12 shed is already wired for electricity if you want to turn it into a workshop.
